  EXPLORER ISN'T SHOWING ALL FILES!
  
   It's not showing all the files in a folder/directory. Select
   View/Options. The first tab ,View, has an option for 'show all
   files.' Change to this option and all files will be displayed from
   then on.
   [6/3/95]
   
   
