  MICROSOFT EXCHANGE WANTS TO LOG INTO MSN EVEN WHEN USED FOR SLIP/PPP
  
   You need to set up a separate profile for Exchange that doesn't
   contain the MSN drivers. To do this, open Control Panel, and select
   the Mail & Fax icon. From there you can create a new profile, and
   only add Internet Mail to it. Be sure to change Exchange to prompt
   you for which profile to use when started.
   [6/3/95]
   
   
